rom other storage backends\n41:     - Caching layer optimizations\n42:     - Valkey Cluster-specific features\n43: \n44: # Acceptance Criteria\n45: acceptance:\n46:   - All Store interface methods implemented for Valkey backend\n47:   - Valkey connection pooling and lifecycle management\n48:   - Proper error translation (valkey nil → ErrNotFound)\n49:   - Atomic pipeline operations for StoreSandbox and DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n50:   - ZSET index management for expiry and activity tracking\n51:   - Environment variable configuration support\n52:   - Unit tests with mocked Valkey client\n53:   - Integration tests with Valkey test server\n54: \n55: # References\n56: references:\n57:   - AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n58:   - AR-013: Redis 存储实现\n59: \n60: # Estimation\n61: estimation:\n62:   size: S\n63:   story_points: 3\n64:   days: 2\n\n(End of file - total 64 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"id: AR-014\ntitle: Valkey 存储实现\nmodule: pkg/store\nlanguage: Go\nsize: S\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-014: Valkey 存储实现\n# Module: pkg/store\n# Language: Go\n# Size: S\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: valkey-storage-implementation","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-014/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775870894173,"end":1775870894195}}}}
