g\n  - Estimated: 2h\n\n- [ ] **T-015**: Add timeout enforcement\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 2h\n\n## Phase 5: Testing\n\n- [ ] **T-016**: Create mock sandbox client\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 2h\n\n- [ ] **T-017**: Write unit tests for Execute\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 4h\n\n- [ ] **T-018**: Write unit tests for async operations\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 3h\n\n- [ ] **T-019**: Write unit tests for status and cancel\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 3h\n\n- [ ] **T-020**: Write integration tests\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 4h\n\n## Summary\n\n- Total tasks: 20\n- Pending: 20\n- In Progress: 0\n- Completed: 0\n- Total estimated: ~41 hours (5 days)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-014/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775871028402,"end":1775871028429}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871028433,"sessionID":"ses_285d8d820ffeeN7duQVkTRpVaN","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2948b7001N93jlnxeKyPrxT","messageID":"msg_d7a2778f7001xyIEXGBK0eMnzb","sessionID":"ses_285d8d820ffeeN7duQVkTRpVaN","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/notes.md","content":"# AR-015: PicoD 命令执行 API - Notes\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n### Execution Model\n\n- Synchronous execution for simple commands\n- Asynchronous execution with status tracking for long-running commands\n- Support for both modes provides flexibility for different use cases\n\n### Resource Limiting\n\n- Resource constraints passed in request\n- Enforcement delegated to sandbox layer\n- API layer validates and passes through\n\n### Output Handling\n\n- Buffer-based output capture for synchronous execution\n- Channel-based streaming for real-time output\n- Size limits to prevent memory issues\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. Should we support command chaining (pipe operations)?\n2. How to handle interactive commands requiring input?\n3. What is the maximum execution queue size?\n4. Should executions be persistent across API restarts?\n\n## References\n\n- AR-009: Sandbox orchestration system\n- AR-012: Session storage interface\n- AR-013: Redis storage implementation\n- AR-014: Valkey storage implementation\n\n## Change Log\n\n| Date | Author | Change |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| 2024-XX-XX | - | Initial scaffold creation |\n\n## Related Documents\n\n- `/design.md` - Architecture and design details\n- `/plan.md` - Implementation plan\n- `/delta-spec.md` - API specification changes\n- `/tests.md` - Test specifications\n- `/tasks.md` - Task breakdown\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-014/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/notes.md","time":{"start":1775871028405,"end":1775871028431}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871028802,"sessionID":"ses_285d8d820ffeeN7duQVkTRpVaN","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2793da0015DFzQ1i7MkHZML","messageID":"msg_d7a2778f7001xyIEXGBK0eMnzb","sessionID":"ses_285d8d820ffeeN7duQVkTRpVaN","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-015\ntitle: PicoD 命令执行 API\nmodule: pkg/picod\nlanguage: Go\nsize: M\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-015: PicoD 命令执行 API\n# Module: pkg/picod\n# Language: Go\n# Size: M\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: picod-command-execution-api\n  description: |\n    Implement the PicoD (Pico Daemon) command execution API that provides\n    a lightweight, sandboxed environment for running commands within agent\n    sessions. PicoD serves as the execution engine for the agentcube platform,\n    enabling secure command isolation, resource limiting, and output streaming\n    capabilities.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - PicoD command execution API definition and implementation\n    - Command request/response protocol design\n    - Sandbox lifecycle management (create, execute, destroy)\n    - Resource limiting (CPU, memory, I/O) integration\n    - Output streaming (stdout/stderr capture)\n    - Error handling and execution status reporting\n    - Security context and privilege isolation\n  out:\n    - Full sandbox orchestration (covered in AR-009)\n    - WebSocket real-time streaming (future enhancement)\n    - Multi-node distributed execution\n    - Custom runtime environments\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - Command execution API with structured request/response\n  - Synchronous and asynchronous execution modes\n  - Resource limit enforcement integration\n  - Output capture and streaming support\n  - Execution status tracking (pending, running, completed, failed)\n  - Timeout and cancellation support\n  - Proper error codes and message propagation\n  - Unit tests for core execution logic\n  - Integration tests with mock sandbox environment\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - AR-009: 沙箱编排系统\n  - AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: M\n  story_points: 5\n  days: 4\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-014/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775871028380,"end":1775871028800}}}}
